description: Triangle read by rows of numbers b_{n,k}, n >= 2, 1 <= k < n such that (1/(1-q*t))*Product_{n,k} 1/(1 - q^n*t^k)^b_{n,k} = Sum_{i,j>=1} S_{i,j} q^i*t^j where S_{i,j} are entries in the table A008277 (the inverse Euler transformation of the table of Stirling numbers of the second kind).
